<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.5.7">
<l>tuppuṭai yāyarkaḷtam colvaḻu vātorukāl</l>
<l rend="indent">tūyaka ruṅkuḻalnal tōkaima yilaṉaiya</l>
<l>nappiṉai taṉtiṟamā nalviṭai yēḻaviya</l>
<l rend="indent">nallati ṟaluṭaiya nātaṉu māṉavaṉē</l>
<l>tappiṉa piḷḷaikaḷait taṉamiku cōtipukat</l>
<l rend="indent">taṉiyoru tērkaṭavit tāyoṭu kūṭṭiyave</l>
<l>ṉappave ṉakkorukā lāṭuka ceṅkīrai</l>
<l rend="indent">yāyarkaḷ pōrēṟē yāṭuka vāṭukavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who became the very powerful husband of Nappiṉai</l>
<l rend="indent">—with curls of pure black, like the beautiful feathers of the peacock—</l>
<l>when, without swerving from the word of the strong cowherds,</l>
<l rend="indent">the seven good bulls perished for [her] sake.</l>
<l>O my Father who, having driven a chariot alone, reunited with [their] mother</l>
<l rend="indent">the children who were lost when [they] entered the great light,</l>
<l rend="indent">dance one time for me!</l>
<l>Battle bull of the cowherds, dance the Ceṅkīrai, please dance!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
